              <p>2.2 Usage Data: In order to gain insights into user interactions and enhance the functionality of our Site, we may collect various types of Usage Data. This includes but is not limited to, log files, IP addresses, device information, device location, and browsing activity. By gathering this information, we aim to gain a better understanding of how users engage with the Site, identify areas for improvement, and optimize its performance. The analysis of Usage Data allows us to enhance the user experience, tailor features to specific user preferences, and ensure the Site meets the evolving needs of our users. Please rest assured that the collection of this data is conducted in accordance with applicable privacy laws and regulations, and all necessary measures are taken to safeguard the confidentiality and security of the collected information.</p>
