              <p>We process your information for purposes based on legitimate business interests, the fulfilment of our contract with you, compliance with our legal obligations, and/or your consent. This information is based on your usage of the app or website. We process your Personal Data for these purposes in reliance on our legitimate business interests to provide our Services, in order to track your usage pattern (“Analytics”), and/or for compliance with our legal obligations (“Legal Purposes”). We indicate the specific processing grounds we rely on next to each purpose listed below.</p>
              <p>3.1 Providing Services: The Personal Data we collect is utilized to facilitate seamless Services and communication between you and us. This includes providing essential features such as call options and relevant information, enabling Users to efficiently connect and interact with each other. Additionally, we employ this Personal Data to maintain and track our Site. By utilizing personal information in this manner, we aim to streamline the user experience, foster productive business relationships with you, and enhance the overall functionality of the Site. We treat all Personal Data with the utmost care and in compliance with applicable privacy laws and regulations, taking appropriate measures to protect its confidentiality and security.</p>
              <p>3.2 Analytics: To continuously enhance the performance and functionality of our Site, we conduct a comprehensive analysis of usage data. This analysis serves multiple purposes, including improving the overall performance of the Site, enriching the quality of data, enhancing the user experience, and optimizing our Services and research purposes. By meticulously examining the usage data, we gain valuable insights into user behaviour, preferences, and patterns of interaction. These insights enable us to identify areas of improvement, refine features, and introduce enhancements that align with user needs and expectations. Additionally, the analysis of usage data allows us to optimize the performance of our Services, ensuring they are efficient, effective, and responsive to user requirements. Rest assured that during the analysis process, we strictly adhere to applicable privacy laws and regulations, safeguarding the confidentiality and anonymity of individual users while utilizing aggregated data to drive continuous improvements within the Site.</p>
              <p>3.3 Legal Purposes: We might use your data usage patterns and information collected from your usage to keep our Site safe and secure by involving technologies related to fraud monitoring and prevention. Apart from this, it may be used to protect our Site for business and/or for legal reasons if a legal request is placed on us.</p>
